{"tid":1512810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要爭取國際介入香港 第一步就係爭取美軍/英軍派醫療艦黎香港","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:47:09.000Z","uid":13663,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"713d2decbe303cbfe05a13e8340fe96a5b0d7c0a","tid":1512810,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"諗諗計"},{"pid":"209ff1bf4d817108215a7b249fc96798b94d2044","tid":1512810,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5427d976ec9dfce87a6792d45b82b8c33ea5d805","tid":1512810,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"海牙公約中對於醫療船的規定是：[1]<br />\n<br />\n醫療船必須用明顯標誌此船為醫療船<br />\n醫療船必須無差別向各國提供醫療照護<br />\n醫療船不得參與任何軍事行動<br />\n醫療船不得干預交戰方船隻的的軍事行動<br />\n交戰方有權登船檢查醫療船是否違反上述行為<br />\n任何武裝的船隻按照法律規定都不能歸類為醫療船。[2]<br />\n<br />\n1949年8月12日日內瓦第二公約《改善海上武裝部隊傷者病者及遇船難者境遇的公約》「第三章　醫院船」。其中第三十五條第一款允許「醫院船或病室之船員為維持秩序，自衛或保護傷者、病者而配有武器」。"},{"pid":"dfcf04dd174a13362484d3c8c06013ec6bd0200d","tid":1512810,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=957c118e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=fc7c4422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=0b7ca9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"25e9c233d92ab9db847cff24306928809327df5f","tid":1512810,"uid":36470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"香港已經發生人道危機，杏林覺醒負荷過重求救，新屋嶺被捕人士集體失憶同骨折，唔記得係邊度受傷，國際救援係有必要而且急切"},{"pid":"212239c9b5c5b71a81eec3e0f8116c4d8d20b05b","tid":1512810,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"英國真係大條道理派船黎<br />\n如果佢當BNO係一回事<br />\n有BNO示威者受傷 可以直接上醫療船"},{"pid":"062faf00eb88e773e1fa5e8b669387009d04b9cf","tid":1512810,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n人手不足<br />\n醫護人員被警方要脅<br />\n人道災難"},{"pid":"3366c552f2d143777baa87f8b7fc09a4a5321da0","tid":1512810,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"軍隊醫療艦都算軍艦，要同中國外交部定國防部申請，呢個時勢邊有可能批，唔通叫人強行進港咩，咁等開戰都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，ngo個d都叫有得諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db583761e0d07d380b7daf764e222622fe2cc3cb","tid":1512810,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cd62811cb612a41165d96cd0ce6c61a4cc7c5d","tid":1512810,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5427d976ec9dfce87a6792d45b82b8c33ea5d805","tid":1512810,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"海牙公約中對於醫療船的規定是：[1]<br />\n<br />\n醫療船必須用明顯標誌此船為醫療船<br />\n醫療船必須無差別向各國提供醫療照護<br />\n醫療船不得參與任何軍事行動<br />\n醫療船不得干預交戰方船隻的的軍事行動<br />\n交戰方有權登船檢查醫療船是否違反上述行為<br />\n任何武裝的船隻按照法律規定都不能歸類為醫療船。[2]<br />\n<br />\n1949年8月12日日內瓦第二公約《改善海上武裝部隊傷者病者及遇船難者境遇的公約》「第三章　醫院船」。其中第三十五條第一款允許「醫院船或病室之船員為維持秩序，自衛或保護傷者、病